webpackJsonp([0xdb26183a937f],{1084:function(t,e){t.exports={data:{wordpressPost:{title:"It&#8217;s Time To STOP Testing Cosmetics On Animals Says The Body Shop",content:'<p>Incredible as it may seem in this day and age, more than 80 per cent of countries throughout the world still have NO laws against the testing of cosmetics on animals. That&#8217;s incredible in and of itself, but even more so when you consider that most countries <strong>do not require safety data</strong> on animal tests and reliable <strong>alternatives are available</strong>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Bottom line &#8211; there is absolutely NO NEED to test cosmetics on animals.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">And yet &#8211; Cruelty Free International, a leading non-profit organisation working to end animal testing, estimates about 500,000 animals are still used in cosmetics testing every year.</p>\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2383 aligncenter" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18184834/MAP-JPG-300x150.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="150" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18184834/MAP-JPG-300x150.jpg 300w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18184834/MAP-JPG-768x383.jpg 768w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18184834/MAP-JPG-1024x511.jpg 1024w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18184834/MAP-JPG.jpg 1535w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" />\n<div class="page" title="Page 1">\n<div class="layoutArea">\n<div class="column">\n<p style="text-align: left;">\n<p style="text-align: left;">The Body Shop hopes to change all that. Accordingly, it launched a new campaign for a <strong>global ban on cosmetics animal testing</strong> on products and ingredients by 2020, revolutionising the beauty industry and protecting millions of animals around the world. The Body Shop will take the campaign to the highest authority, the United Nations, and request an international convention banning cosmetics testing on animals once and for all.</p>\n<div class="page" title="Page 1">\n<div class="layoutArea">\n<div class="column" style="text-align: left;">\n<p>Jessie Macneil-Brown, Senior Manager International Campaigns and Corporate Responsibility, The Body Shop, says: “The Body Shop passionately believes that no animal should be harmed in the name of cosmetics and that animal testing on products and ingredients is outdated, cruel and unnecessary.</p>\n</div>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img class="size-medium wp-image-2385 alignnone" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18185428/all-in-one-instablur-74793-150x300.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18185428/all-in-one-instablur-74793-150x300.jpg 150w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18185428/all-in-one-instablur-74793-768x1539.jpg 768w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18185428/all-in-one-instablur-74793-511x1024.jpg 511w" sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" /><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2386" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18185457/all-in-one-cheek-colour-56507-229x300.jpg" alt="" width="229" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18185457/all-in-one-cheek-colour-56507-229x300.jpg 229w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18185457/all-in-one-cheek-colour-56507-768x1008.jpg 768w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18185457/all-in-one-cheek-colour-56507-780x1024.jpg 780w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18185457/all-in-one-cheek-colour-56507.jpg 1350w" sizes="(max-width: 229px) 100vw, 229px" /><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2387" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18185522/all-in-one-face-base-30164-247x300.jpg" alt="" width="247" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18185522/all-in-one-face-base-30164-247x300.jpg 247w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18185522/all-in-one-face-base-30164-768x934.jpg 768w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18185522/all-in-one-face-base-30164.jpg 822w" sizes="(max-width: 247px) 100vw, 247px" /></p>\n<div class="column">\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Head to The Body Shop and support the group by buying an ace product or three. Try <a href="http://www.thebodyshop.com.au/make-up/all-in-one-make-up/all-in-one-instablur#.WUZAyzN7FBw">All-In-One InstaBlur, $25</a>, cause it&#8217;s awesome. Same goes for <a href="http://www.thebodyshop.com.au/make-up/cheek-colour/all-in-one-cheek-colour#.WUZArTN7FBw">All-In-One Cheek Colour, $19</a>, and <a href="http://www.thebodyshop.com.au/make-up/foundation-and-powder/all-in-one-face-base#.WUZAijN7FBw">All-In-One Face Base, $29</a>.</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">&#8220;This is why The Body Shop and Cruelty Free International have partnered to deliver the largest and most ambitious campaign ever to seek a global ban on the use of animals to test cosmetic products and ingredients.&#8221;</p>\n<div class="page" title="Page 2">\n<div class="layoutArea">\n<div class="column">\n<p style="text-align: left;">The bold beauty brand&#8217;s campaign aims to engage eight million people to sign the petition calling on the United Nations to introduce an international convention to end the practice once and for all. If you want to get on board (and we recommend you do) the petition can be signed<a href="https://www.e-activist.com/page/9583/petition/1?utm_source=vanity&amp;utm_medium=print&amp;utm_campaign=ww_170601_w22_cta_faat-petition"> online</a> or at any of The Body Shop’s 3,000 stores across the world.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">You can also use the campaign hashtag, #ForeverAgainstAnimalTesting, on social media to raise awareness of the issue.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n',better_featured_image:{source_url:"http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18171237/JPG-conejitoseveryday.jpg"},categories:[{slug:"beauty-talk",name:"Beauty Talk"}]},site:{siteMetadata:{title:"The Beauty Insider"}}},pathContext:{id:"8b788f4e-4be6-52d7-a367-831a9dfda29a"}}}});
//# sourceMappingURL=path---time-stop-testing-cosmetics-animals-stops-says-body-shop-49b204573ec19dccd9e2.js.map